1) Create a simple login system.
    It should include username and password
    The password should include: length- 8
                                 must contain- @

- Run a loop in case the user does not meet the conditions (If Else)
- Ask user for the details to match stored details (.equals)
- Check if the password has:
  -8 letters using if .length() >= 8
  -symbol'@' using .indexOf()
- If -1 is returned then ask the user to try again
- If anything other than - 1 is returned then Login successful.

2) Create a simple search in a string.
-Ask user for string to search into
-run if else
-use .contain to check if the string us there or not

3) WAP to count the number of vowels and constant in a string.
